every hour using a time-weighted average price between the perpetual and mark price. The vAMM model incorporates JIT liquidity auctions to reduce slippage during funding settlements. Positions automatically pay or receive funding based on the rate sign, with settlements occurring seamlessly through Drift's on-chain infrastructure. The hybrid model ensures funding rates reflect true market imbalances while maintaining capital efficiency."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
